# Internal dev-tracking docs (decision log + build tracker + gap-discovery findings) — same
# approach as ../testFlow's own .gitignore: not part of the public project, local planning
# artifacts only. Wildcarded (was: individually-named PLAN_*.md entries) after PLAN_LIFECYCLE.md
# turned up as an untracked straggler with no matching rule — every PLAN_*.md is local-only now,
# no case-by-case exceptions (PLAN_GAPS_16_17.md was one; untracked via `git rm --cached` in the
# same change that added this line).
PLAN.md
plan_v2.md
PLAN_*.md
PROGRESS.md
TFLW-GAPS.md
TFLW-FEATURE-GAPS.md
HELPERS.md
